ccre.util

Class CHashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.util.CHashMap<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type.
    V - the value type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<K>

    public final class CHashMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<K>
    A basic hash map. Iterate over this to iterate over all the keys. Does not support null keys, but does support null values.
    Author:
    skeggsc
